# Every change to the default branch requires review from the human maintainer.
#
# The coding agent runs as the github-actions bot, which is NOT a code owner —
# so it can OPEN pull requests, but its review can never satisfy the required
# code-owner approval. A human must approve before merge. (GitHub bundles
# "create and approve PRs" into one Actions setting, so this branch rule is how
# we guarantee the agent can never approve/merge its own work.)
